{"tid":2076324,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［警世］民研公佈最新特首民望  上升逾10分","createTime":"2020-06-23T12:12:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-23T14:54:38.000Z","uid":358086,"like":6,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"0e504563c407ae4694c619a7fe9ce13b852e8489","tid":2076324,"uid":358086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T12:12:46.000Z","msg":"林鄭評分升<br />\n學者：市民將責任歸咎於中央非港府<br />\n<br />\n教大社會科學系講師吳凱宇指，<span style=\"color: red;\">林鄭評分由今年2月的18分，上升至現時的29分，形容上升逾10分「係一個唔細嘅數字」。</span>他指，2月評分較低或與港府遲遲未願封關有關，惟現時疫情受控，加上一系列新措施，如「保就業」計劃、派錢等，令市民不滿減少。<br />\n<br />\n即使「港版國安法」如箭在弦，吳指評分反映市民「將責任歸咎畀中央政府，唔係歸咎畀特區政府，可能知道佢哋都無得決定」，但認為國安法將令林鄭評分未能有更多的上升空間。<br />\n<br />\n香港民意研究所副行政總裁鍾劍華補充，是次調查於6月18日完結，惟同日才有報道指，港區國安法草案已由全國人大委員長會議提請常委會審議，因此國安法對政府民望的影響，或需留待下次民調才能有效反映。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200623/4XEBCGSSZW4ACIA7VSQ3IDAOZU/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200623%2F4XEBCGSSZW4ACIA7VSQ3IDAOZU%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=91nyg34XrGq4aGOua7i4Jf%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=5ab45a10\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200623%2F4XEBCGSSZW4ACIA7VSQ3IDAOZU%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=be41c111\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200623/4XEBCGSSZW4ACIA7VSQ3IDAOZU/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9950cf5e7708c32